      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, i need help writing a formal email to one of our warehouse employees. they've been showing up about 15 mins late to every shift for the last two weeks. i need to let them know it's a problem and that we need to see improvement, but i don't want to sound like i'm attacking them or anything. just a firm but professional warning. can you draft something?",
