      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Addressing Shift Timeliness\n\nDear [Employee's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I wanted to take a moment to discuss a matter that has come to our attention regarding your recent shift arrivals. As you may know, punctuality is a key component of our team's success, and consistent tardiness can impact our operations.\n\nWe understand that unforeseen circumstances can occasionally cause delays, but it is important to strive for punctuality as much as possible. Over the past two weeks, we have noticed that your arrival times have been consistently 15 minutes past the scheduled start of your shifts. While we appreciate your dedication and hard work, we would like to address this issue to ensure it does not continue.\n\nWe value your contributions and believe that with a little adjustment, we can work together to improve your punctuality. We are confident that you can meet this expectation and continue to be a valuable member of our team.\n\nThank you for your understanding and cooperation. Please feel free to reach out if you have any concerns or if there are any underlying issues that we can address together.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Company Name]",
