      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Urgent: Addressing Shift Timeliness Concerns\n\nDear [Employee's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I am writing to you with a matter of some urgency regarding your recent shift arrivals. As you may be aware, punctuality is a fundamental aspect of our team's success, and consistent tardiness can significantly impact our operations.\n\nOver the past two weeks, we have observed that your arrival times have been consistently 15 minutes past the scheduled start of your shifts. While we understand that unforeseen circumstances can occasionally cause delays, it is crucial to strive for punctuality as much as possible. We value your dedication and hard work, but we must address this issue to ensure it does not continue.\n\nWe would like to emphasize that this is not a casual heads-up, but a serious warning. If this pattern of tardiness persists, we will have to consider formal disciplinary action. We believe that with a little adjustment, we can work together to improve your punctuality and continue to be a valuable member of our team.\n\nThank you for your understanding and cooperation. Please feel free to reach out if you have any concerns or if there are any underlying issues that we can address together.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]",
